ran there after your call?

43
00:04:25,500 --> 00:04:28,300
Then send Seo Dong-jae at least.

44
00:04:28,420 --> 00:04:30,920
- CEO Nam.
- Just send him as I say, damn it!

45
00:04:33,970 --> 00:04:35,390
No.

46
