near your location.

61
00:05:22,100 --> 00:05:24,480
What? Gun death?

62
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:26,690
It's a restricted
development site.

63
00:05:26,810 --> 00:05:29,520
You're the closest.
You should go check.

64
00:05:30,110 --> 00:05:31,110
Me?

65
00:05:31,650 --> 00:05:32,990
Okay.

66
00:05:33,110 --> 00:05:35,740
I'm on my way. Yes.

67
00:05:35,860 --> 00:05:36,820
Bye.

68
00:05:40,290 --> 00:05:42,830
