so we captured him right away.

80
00:07:13,380 --> 00:07:15,550
Here? Next to the body?

81
00:07:15,670 --> 00:07:16,720
- Yes.
- Okay.

82
00:07:17,800 --> 00:07:19,720
- What's the weapon?
- A shotgun.

83
00:07:19,840 --> 00:07:20,800
A shotgun?

84
00:07:21,760 --> 00:07:23,010
