after getting shot in her back.

98
00:08:10,810 --> 00:08:11,850
A shotgun.

99
00:08:17,030 --> 00:08:18,440
A shotgun?

100
00:08:23,700 --> 00:08:24,910
Then was it...

101
00:08:26,790 --> 00:08:29,290
